  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stream Arenas is only played on Twitch</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/e9f05cb5d09f2861b5e1446b5a31fd96.poster.avif?t=1623342151\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/e9f05cb5d09f2861b5e1446b5a31fd96.webm?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/e9f05cb5d09f2861b5e1446b5a31fd96.mp4?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Stream Arenas</strong> is an interactive Twitch game where you transform your Twitch chat into fierce Chatiators!  Go head to head with the community and battle your way to the top of each Season to be the ultimate Chatiator!  Fight your opponents using a multitude of characters with unique special moves in a variety of different arenas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/d27368927a26c5247bea323219a884a1.poster.avif?t=1623342151\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/d27368927a26c5247bea323219a884a1.webm?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/d27368927a26c5247bea323219a884a1.mp4?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Weekly and Seasonal Leaderboards with in-game rewards for viewers and Streamers<br></li><li> Unique Bosses and Beasts, get rewarded for taking them down<br></li><li> Characters that play differently, with different classes, and ultimate attacks<br></li><li> Huge assortment of Arenas <br></li><li> Streamer Rewards<br></li><li> Tournaments <br></li><li> In-game Events<br></li><li> A long road map with very active development! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/2de285f94dded5908acc70f715bf73f0.poster.avif?t=1623342151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/2de285f94dded5908acc70f715bf73f0.webm?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390300/extras/2de285f94dded5908acc70f715bf73f0.mp4?t=1623342151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twitch Engagement</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Spawn Events in the game with bits and subscriptions! <br></li><li> Channel Point integration<br></li><li> Chat commands to take complete control of your characters<br></li><li> In-game drops for taking down chests! </li></ul>",
